    "Suri-SFT for coherent and informative constraint satisfaction.",
    "In this evaluation, we are interested in how our fine-tuned models satisfy constraints in Suri.",
    "We ask two annotators to compare text generations from Suri-SFT and Suri-I-ORPO with respect to a given constraint based on the following criteria:",
    "• Informativeness: Which generation provides more details about the constraint?",
    "• Coherence: Which generation effectively integrates the constraint with the rest of the text?"
